OL,3,CWhale stranded in Baltic Sea swims
OL,4,Cfree under 'police escort'
OL,6,FA humpback whale stranded for days in
OL,7,Fshallow water off the coast of Germany
OL,8,Fand given a very slim chance of
OL,9,Fsurvival, has swam free - but it is
OL,10,Fnot out of danger yet.
OL,12,FThe marine mammal, assumed to be a
OL,13,Fyoung male, became stuck on an
OL,14,F"underwater ramp" near the Baltic Sea
OL,15,Fresort of Timmendorfer Strand, off the
OL,16,Fnorthern coast of Germany, on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
