OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774649478
OL,3,CWhale stranded in Baltic Sea swims
OL,4,Cfree under 'police escort'
OL,6,FMarine biologist Robert Marc Lehmann,
OL,7,Fwho accompanied the operation, gave
OL,8,Fthe whale 0.1% chance of survival
OL,9,Fearlier this week, stating that it was
OL,10,Fin the "worst possible position" and
OL,11,Fhad a rope hanging from its mouth.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
