PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774649478
OL,3,CWhale stranded in Baltic Sea swims
OL,4,Cfree under 'police escort'
OL,6,FBut an excavator spent Thursday
OL,7,Fdigging an escape channel near the
OL,8,Fwhale's head, enabling the animal to
OL,9,Fswim through it overnight, Lehmann
OL,10,Fconfirmed on Friday.
OL,12,FHe cautioned that the whale, which is
OL,13,F12 to 15 metres long, will only really
OL,14,Fbe at home again if it reaches the
OL,15,Fopen Atlantic Ocean - some 600
OL,16,Fnautical miles away.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
