PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774649478
OL,3,CWhale stranded in Baltic Sea swims
OL,4,Cfree under 'police escort'
OL,6,FThe whale is under a "police escort"
OL,7,Fwith support from at least six
OL,8,Fvessels, including the coast guard and
OL,9,Fthe German Life Saving Association
OL,10,F(DLRG), as it swims through Danish
OL,11,Fwaters.
OL,13,F"I'm cautiously optimistic. The whale
OL,14,Fis in poor health," Lehmann said.
OL,16,F"Its skin looks bad, it's weak, and it
OL,17,Fhasn't eaten in a long time."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
