PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774649478
OL,3,CWhale stranded in Baltic Sea swims
OL,4,Cfree under 'police escort'
OL,6,FThe whale was spotted stuck on an
OL,7,Funderwater sandbank on Monday morning,
OL,8,Fand initial efforts to free it and
OL,9,Fcoax it back toward deeper water,
OL,10,Fincluding using coast guard and fire
OL,11,Fdepartment boats to create large
OL,12,Fwaves, were unsuccessful.
OL,14,FHumpback whales are not native to the
OL,15,FBaltic Sea, which lacks strong tides
OL,16,Fthat could have helped the stranded
OL,17,Fwhale to free itself.
OL,19,FLehmann told reporters on Thursday
OL,20,Fthat the whale was reacting but was
OL,21,Fvisibly suffering.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
